This project explores the Crime Cast Forecasting dataset to predict crime categories using machine learning models like Decision Tree and Random Forest. It includes data cleaning, EDA, feature engineering, model training, evaluation, and hyperparameter tuning.

Tech Stack / Libraries
  Python,pandas,numpy,matplotlib / seaborn,scikit-learn

Workflow
  1.Data Loading
  2.Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
  3.Data Cleaning & Preprocessing
  4.Feature Engineering
  5.Model Building (Random Forest, Decision Tree)
  6.Cross-validation & Hyperparameter Tuning
  7.Evaluation
